ved : Css & rtl arabic\r\n		- Improved: Twitter Counter function .\r\n		- Improved: Twitter widget .\r\n		- And other improvements and minor bug fixes.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n		<h2> version 3.4.0 - 09-09-2013 </h2>\r\n		- NEW FEATURE: Add Google+ (Followers) to Widget Social counter\r\n		- NEW FEATURE: Add Soundcloud (Followers) to Widget Social counter \r\n		- NEW FEATURE: Add Soundcloud to Shortcode\r\n		- NEW FEATURE: Add Google maps to Shortcode\r\n		- NEW FEATURE: Widget Social counter 4 Style design\r\n		- NEW FEATURE: Add RelatedPosts widgets\r\n		- And other improvements and minor bug fixes.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n        <h1> BEFORE UPDATING TO 3.3.0 </h1>\r\n        Hello,\r\n        *Before the update to Version 3.3.0 :\r\n\r\n        - Make a backup of the Theme inside your WordPress installation folder /wp-content/cherry .\r\n        - Update the theme via ftp or wordpress dashboard .\r\n        - After updating empty your blog cache you if use any cache or CDN plugin .\r\n        - Empty your browser cache .\r\n\r\n        * Please check all the settings again .\r\n        * Please note that:\r\n        - The Short codes AND The Widgets ( Has fully programmed again ) To avoid any conflict with the version wordpress 3.6 .\r\n\r\n        * Please be aware that we are working on what is always better for your convenience .\r\n\r\n		<h2> version 3.3.0 - 04-09-2013 </h2>\r\n\r\n        - Fully Supports New Wordpress 3.6 .\r\n        - Fixed: Short codes\r\n        - Fixed: All Widgets\r\n        - And other improvements and minor bug fixes.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n		<h2> version 3.2.0 - 28-08-2013 </h2>\r\n		- NEW FEATURE: Top Footer Home Page Simplified view of Categories\r\n		- improvements and minor bug fixes.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n		<h2> version 3.1.0 - 21-08-2013 </h2>\r\n		\r\n		- Fixed : cycle slider\r\n		- And other improvements and minor bug fixes.\r\n		\r\n		\r\n		\r\n		============================================\r\n		\r\n		<h2>version 3.0.0 - 17-08-2013</h2>\r\n		\r\n		- Improved : Theme Speed and performance .\r\n		- And other improvements and minor bug fixes.\r\n		- Please replace whole folder. We changed too many files in this version.\r\n		\r\n		\r\n\r\n		============================================\r\n		\r\n	\r\n		<h2>version 2.4.0 - 02-07-2013</h2>\r\n\r\n		- NEW FEATURE: dribbble Followers - widget social counter\r\n		- NEW FEATURE: vimeo Subscribers - widget social counter\r\n		- NEW FEATURE: Schema Search Microdata\r\n		- Improved: All Twitter API Error messages moved to the backend .\r\n		- Updated : Theme functions to use Twitter Api 1.1 .\r\n		- And other improvements and minor bug fixes.\r\n		\r\n\r\n		<h2>version 2.3.0 - 30-4-2013</h2>\r\n		-Improvements and minor bug fixes.\r\n\r\n\r\n		<h2>version 2.2.0 - 18-3-2013</h2>\r\n		- Added         :   Widget Youtube Channel .\r\n		- Added         :   Widget Slider Posts .\r\n		- Added 		: 	Option to Hide Top Menu .\r\n		- Added 		: 	Option to Display posts excerpt + Full width featured image.\r\n		- Added 		: 	Option to show featured image and gallery with lightbox in post head area  .\r\n		- Added 		:	New layout style for the New in picture box .\r\n		- Added			:	Option to disable Notify On Theme Updates .\r\n		\r\n		- Improvements and minor bug fixes.\r\n		\r\n		- Improved		: 	Responsive layout .\r\n		- Improved 		: 	Compatibility with twitter api 1.1 .\r\n		- Improved 		: 	Scroll to top icon animation .\r\n		- Improved 		: 	Social Counter Function .\r\n		- Fixed 		:	Theme Panel .\r\n		\r\n        <h2>version 2.1.0 - 15-1-2013</h2>\r\n        - Added         :     Top Today Date ( Option ON/OFF - Today Date Format <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://codex.wordpress.org/Formatting_Date_and_Time\" original-title=\"\">Documentation on date and time formatting</a>  )\r\n        - Added         :     Stick The Navigation Menu  ( Option ON/OFF )\r\n        - Added         :     Stick The Article Pagination Right/Left  ( Option ON/OFF )\r\n        - Improved 		:	  Blog Home\r\n        - Improved 		:     Featured images sizes\r\n        - Improved 		:     RTL\r\n\r\n\r\n		<h2>version 2.0.0 - 23-1-2013</h2>\r\n		- Added         :     Google Fonts - Typography ( Option to Choose - Font Color / Font Size / Font Name / Font weight / Font Style ) .\r\n		- Improved     	:     More Increase the Theme speed\r\n		- Improved     	:     SEO\r\n\r\n\r\n        <h2>version 1.9.0 - 21-1-2013</h2>\r\n        - Fixed 		:	RTL Support ( Arabic ) .\r\n		- Fixed 		: 	Responsive bug .\r\n		- Fixed 		: 	Slider.\r\n		- Fixed 		: 	Background Custom ( with Option to Pattern /  Custom Background )\r\n		- Improved 		:	SEO.\r\n		- Added 		: 	Blog Home Social Shares Buttons\r\n\r\n		<h2>version 1.8.0 - 17-1-2013</h2>\r\n         - Added 		: 	Translation Ready .\r\n		- Added 		:	RTL Support ( Arabic )\r\n		- Added 		:	Flexslider Home\r\n		- Added 		:	More Slider Settings\r\n		- Added 		:	Post Formats Video\r\n		- Added 		:	Post Formats Slider\r\n		- Added 		:	Post Formats With Featured Image\r\n		- Added 		:	Youtube Subscribers To Widget\r\n		- Fixed 		: 	Full Pages Responsive bug .\r\n		- Added 		: 	Responsive ( with Option to Disable it ) .\r\n\r\n		<h2>version 1.7.0 - 10-1-2013</h2>\r\n		- Added 		:	More Social Icons\r\n		- Improved 	:	Aqua Resizer (Resizes WordPress images on the fly).\r\n\r\n		<h2>version 1.6.0 - 8-1-2013</h2>\r\n		- Added 		:	Slider/Newsletter  Fully customizable (Lates-Category-Tags) .\r\n		- Added 		:	Logo/Headerads Margin Top customizable .\r\n		- Added 		:	728 × 90 banner as option in header\r\n		- Added 		:	Using Timthumb ON/OFF .\r\n		- Added 		:	Aqua Resizer (Resizes WordPress images on the fly).\r\n		- Fixed 		:	Images Caption Style\r\n		- Fixed 		:	Newsletter/Slider\r\n\r\n		<h2>version 1.5.0 - 4-1-2013</h2>\r\n		- Added 		:	Blogging Page Amazing  Post Format (Gallery/Video/Quote/Link)\r\n\r\n		<h2>version 1.4.0 - 2-1-2013</h2>\r\n		- Fixed 		:	Related Posts Improved , custom view (Category/Tags)\r\n		- Improved 	: 	More Increase the Theme speed\r\n\r\n\r\n		<h2>version 1.3.0 - 29-12-2012</h2>\r\n		- Added 		:	Posts Ratings\r\n		- Added 		:	Admin Posts Thumbnails\r\n		- Added 		:	Video Posts Thumbnails\r\n\r\n\r\n		<h2>version 1.2.0 - 28-12-2012</h2>\r\n		- Added 		:	widget Ads 120x90\r\n		- Added			:	widget Ads 125x125\r\n		- Added 		:	widget Ads 160x600\r\n		- Added 		:	widget Ads 250x250\r\n		- Added 		:	widget Ads 280x250\r\n		- Fixed 		:	Slider bug\r\n		- Fixed 		:	Panel slow submit problem\r\n		- Fixed 		:	Max panel submit work with ajax\r\n		- Improved 	: 	Styling Options\r\n		- Improved 	:	Responsive issues\r\n\r\n\r\n		<h2>version 1.1.0 - 26-12-2012</h2>\r\n		- Edit Slider\r\n		- Add Blog List Page\r\n\r\n\r\n		]]>\r\n	</changelog>\r\n</notifier>\r\n','yes'),(45332,'notifier-cache-last-updated','1422531367','yes'),(65757,'nonce_key','r`?:~Ay}@P(#p%MV:M2M|7s{*U,G+tIwww(vD0O.HD>(+^If(/RBs<;1o:r(m|O.','yes'),(65758,'nonce_salt','Jx@AEm]Teoi(o-i87/;7p3JHQsDJ2zN0-S7.12iWe,?Z%SNmb(~K*/8 ^8.=FVuo','yes'),(65753,'finished_splitting_shared_terms','1','yes'),(65754,'_split_terms','a:2:{i:27;a:1:{s:8:\"post_tag\";i:82;}i:47;a:1:{s:8:\"post_tag\";i:83;}}','yes'),(65759,'site_icon','27293','yes'),(65760,'medium_large_size_w','768','yes'),(65761,'medium_large_size_h','0','yes'),(65763,'auth_key','z+}++`lq2.Un:j/eD>xY.phEy]unuJ??rr)~cd<fj#Z El5a0,vb^zmJqQBf&- }','yes'),(65764,'auth_salt','^EIg|W/GTeq7&iLBoyPyA;pPypC*04u)koP:VgS_=p_Q0f8P2Ax(U?W>MS/|okyH','yes'),(65765,'logged_in_key','Zi}4B-<Q5$&u~VHUyw<.u9?Exgd+6~r`uv7[(#Paq)jzq1;<<+caBW<vgGz.-yrM','yes'),(65766,'logged_in_salt','9N!aq-vcvCv+mnEP3HbJ`QuB//1m!jC2d}#VOA+%}#5ZE`In@n(|zbw&KR@1]i[P','yes'),(72909,'fresh_site','0','off'),(77335,'widget_custom_html','a:1:{s:12:\"_multiwidget\";i:1;}','yes'),(82702,'stats_cache','a:1:{s:32:\"250dc4c4fe811241bc998b80f61f5a44\";a:1:{i:1747474987;a:0:{}}}','yes'),(188269,'w3tc_generic_widgetservices','{\"content\":{\"items\":[{\"name\":\"Premium Support Response (Usually <1h First Response)\",\"parameter_name\":\"field4\"